<li><a href="/wiki/Alex_Proyas" title="Alex Proyas">Alex Proyas</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Knowing_(film)" title="Knowing (film)">Knowing</a></i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Anthony_Hopkins" title="Anthony Hopkins">Anthony Hopkins</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Slipstream_(2007_film)" title="Slipstream (2007 film)">Slipstream</a></i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Peter_Jackson" title="Peter Jackson">Peter Jackson</a> – <a href="/wiki/Crossing_the_Line_(short)" title="Crossing the Line (short)">Crossing the Line</a></li>
