<li><a href="/wiki/Sidney_Lumet" title="Sidney Lumet">Sidney Lumet</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Before_the_Devil_Knows_You%27re_Dead" title="Before the Devil Knows You're Dead">Before the Devil Knows You're Dead</a></i></li>
