<li><a href="/wiki/Michael_Mann_(director)" title="Michael Mann (director)">Michael Mann</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Miami_Vice_(film)" title="Miami Vice (film)">Miami Vice</a></i>, <i><a href="/wiki/Collateral_(film)" title="Collateral (film)">Collateral</a>, <a href="/wiki/Public_Enemies" title="Public Enemies" class="mw-redirect">Public Enemies</a></i></li>
